Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
By the solution to the TMP on the isolated cubic, if the measure exists, then \
the atom (0,0) (corresponding to +/-I) must have density 2 and Mom-2M_(0,0), \
where M_(0,0) is the moment matrix generated by the atom (0,0) has a measure. \
Further, Mom-2M_(0,0) has a measure if the Rank of N is equal to its rank \
without the its last row/column.\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.987637560597849*^9, 3.987637666828766*^9}, {
  3.987637717557974*^9, 3.9876377756983337`*^9}, {3.987638690913273*^9, 
  3.9876387190278263`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"93ea2885-9ff1-ec45-bff3-\
ece9011181d4"],

